            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dr. DIS provides a \"feel like home\" experience for children, with wonderful teachers who nurture students to their best potential. The campus boasts excellent infrastructure and amenities, fostering growth in every possible way.\n\nThe management excels in training the faculty, ensuring top-notch teaching materials. The school not only educates students academically but also shapes them into good citizens, offering value-based education beyond textbooks.\n\nThe teachers are always willing to go the extra mile to help my child learn and succeed. I am truly grateful for their dedication and hard work.\n\nThe most impressive aspect is the holistic learning approach, which makes my child joyful about attending school. I strongly recommend Dr. DIS to new parents seeking balanced and comprehensive education for their children.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Dr.Dasarathan International School - Singanallur"
          },
          "author": {
