            "name": "Nave Pras"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-06-04",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hearty appreciations to the dynamic management and all the lovely teachers for their meticulous efforts in fostering the overall growth and development of my child. Your play based learning approach is  amazing. Thank you for instilling this love for learning. We are so glad to see the progress in her civility and healthy food habits as well. This is a top-notch institution for the children.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
