            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "*I am eternally grateful for your support in helping my son become the best version of himself.\n*I am impressed with your curriculum and teaching methods which is different from other schools. Well planned worksheets for practice makes my child think beyond prescribed Textbooks. I like to take this privilege to congratulate the management of the School for its endless efforts.\n*\" The Staff and Principal are very polite and cooperative and the best part is that the school is using different learning styles like smart boards which makes learning fun for all students\".\n*I am glad about the mentors who mould my son for the better future.",
          "publisher": {
